    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "it just feels so heavy. like, the effort it takes to just exist, to eat, to work, to deal with people... it feels like I'm spending all this energy to maintain something that has no actual value. if the outcome is always going to be zero, doesn't it make sense to just stop fighting it? why keep pretending there's a reason to struggle through it all?",
